Brazil - Bahia State League 1997


Obs.: The Itabuna team which played this championship is Itabuna Atlético Clube
(colors: yellow and black) which has nothing to do with the most traditional
Itabuna Esporte Clube (colors: blue and white).

First Stage

First Phase

[Every club plays those of the other group.]

Round 1 [Jan 26]
Itabuna        1-0 Eunapolis
Conquista      0-3 Catuense
Fluminense     0-2 Pocoes
Jequie         0-2 Galicia
Ypiranga       2-2 Juazeiro
Vitoria        4-0 River
Bahia          2-0 Sao Francisco

Round 2
Bahia          5-1 Conquista
Ypiranga       3-1 Galicia
Eunapolis      1-4 Vitoria
Itabuna        1-1 Jequie
Catuense       3-2 Fluminense
Sao Francisco  0-0 Pocoes
River          1-4 Juazeiro

Round 3 [Feb 16]
Juazeiro       1-3 Bahia
River          0-0 Itabuna
Galicia        2-1 Pocoes
Vitoria        1-0 Catuense
Sao Francisco  2-1 Eunapolis
Jequie         0-0 Conquista
Fluminense     2-1 Ypiranga

Round 4
Bahia          0-3 Vitoria
Catuense       1-3 Galicia
Conquista      1-1 River
Eunapolis      2-2 Fluminense
Pocoes         1-0 Itabuna
Jequie         0-1 Juazeiro
Sao Francisco  2-1 Ypiranga

Round 5 [Mar 2]
Eunapolis      1-1 Galicia
Ypiranga       1-8 Vitoria
Itabuna        1-3 Bahia
River          0-1 Sao Francisco
Fluminense     1-0 Jequie
Juazeiro       0-0 Catuense
Pocoes         1-2 Conquista

Round 6 [Mar 9]
Jequie         0-1 Sao Francisco
Conquista      0-0 Ypiranga
Itabuna        1-1 Catuense
Juazeiro       1-2 Eunapolis
Fluminense     2-2 River
[Mar 10]
Galicia        0-1 Bahia
[Mar 14]
Vitoria        2-2 Pocoes
 
Round 7 [Mar 16]
Bahia          2-0 Fluminense
Vitoria        4-0 Jequie
Pocoes         2-0 Juazeiro
Catuense       0-0 Sao Francisco
River          0-1 Galicia
Ypiranga       2-0 Itabuna
Conquista      1-0 Eunapolis

