Semi-Finals:

First Leg [Mar 23]
Sao Francisco  0-1 Bahia
Pocoes         0-3 Vitoria

Second Leg [Mar 30]
Bahia          5-1 Sao Francisco
Vitoria        2-0 Pocoes

Final:

First Leg [Apr 6]
Bahia          2-4 Vitoria

Second Leg [Apr 13]
Vitoria        1-3 Bahia

Vitoria wins first stage.


