Group B:
 1.Bahia         7  3  3  1  10- 5   12
 2.Poções        7  2  3  2   8- 9    9
 3.Ypiranga      7  2  2  3   8-11    8
 4.Catuense      7  2  2  3   7-10    8
 5.Eunápolis     7  2  2  3   9-16    8
 6.River         7  1  2  4   7-10    5
 7.Jequié        7  1  1  5   5-10    4

Relegated: Itabuna, River, and Jequié.

Semifinals 

First Leg [May 28]
Juazeiro       1-1 Bahia
Pocoes         0-4 Vitoria
 
Semifinals
Second Leg [May 31]
Bahia          4-2 Juazeiro
Vitoria        2-1 Pocoes

Final

First Leg
Bahia          0-3 Vitoria

Second Leg
Vitoria        0-1 Bahia

Vitoria wins second stage.

Vitória 1997 Bahia champions due to had won both stages.

Topscorer: Agnaldo (Vitória) 15 goals.


